Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢冈崎君 请跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 很抱歉 你一定很困扰对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然听到这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不说出来我会很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们也才刚认识不久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然经常有跟杏三个人一起吃吃饭什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是说我讨厌你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说从没当作恋爱对象看待过呢 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 这种说法很失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样也不介意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试着交往看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下来会逐渐了解对方的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得接下来的时间不是作为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作为男女朋友来度过的话可能也不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起你就是我的女朋友了 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 眼泪 控制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是做梦一样 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的志愿是护士学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那是我从小的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对将来的事完全没考虑过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我认为不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行 如果整天游手好闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会被你讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事绝不可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事 我都不会讨厌冈崎君的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还从没有人对我说过这样的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点感动了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 杏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好的星期天你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好陪在椋身边怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别瞎操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从二年级开始就一直喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你觉得你们能好好发展下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能行吧 她又认真又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸动不动就红 所以稍微让人有点担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 不过她的这种地方也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 你可真是什么事都想着妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不尽是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟椋接过吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 才 才没做过那种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行 你要更主动一些才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说… 我可是第一次跟女生交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就把我当成椋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是双胞胎 感觉上也很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是练习 真亲了可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你刚才当真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你个及格分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是在那公园里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎不就是那个不良少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那两人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们原来是同班 而且现在关系似乎也很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎样也不能在那种地方 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就没一点羞耻感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊 冈崎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么连你也这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 我跟杏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.91,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在走廊里跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经传遍整个学校了 说你昨天跟杏接了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 不 那个该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么一回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 我也觉得你最近不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说了我没做过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说跟我交往的是她妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 你跟藤林椋？ 真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么意外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们俩性格完全不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是杏的话我倒还能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这传闻藤林估计也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只要在学校就算不想听也会传进耳朵里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在这儿在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下 不会浪费你太多时间的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛… 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什么也没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 说实话确实是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 我所说的话就那么奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 一直以来不是从来都没有过这种感觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是那个吧 因为过于接近而无法察觉的心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 让你见识一下显而易见的证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪啊 你真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说错了的话我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 你应该是喜欢冈崎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 想消除自己跟你的流言才想跟我交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流言什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是流言的话 何必做到这种地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 阳平说过的话你可别当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你跟椋关系那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想着「我也交个男朋友多好」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就想干脆就找阳平好了 于是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道因为这么简单的理由就去找男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是多管什么闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想着椋的事就行了 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女朋友担心的男人最差劲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共八百日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试着叫叫你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 像杏还不是直呼我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 都已经是这种关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的话也叫我椋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋 朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去春原那儿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是星期天 没人会来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牡丹 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你不是跟椋去约会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都完全湿透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想着椋的事就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你是椋的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在跟这些没关系吧 你会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要管我 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我这么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个笨蛋 你对我温柔的话我会误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕 害怕去告白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果向你告白 被拒绝了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就连朋友也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和你交往了 又会让椋伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 还不如放弃了好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有这样才不会有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我现在心里只有后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是笨呢 明明是自己已经决定了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤林杏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是椋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也的确是个难题呢 在双胞胎之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你 会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我站在你的立场上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还有什么好说的 自然是两人都要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把你揍到爬不起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说真的 确实是很难办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想跟双方都保持距离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就真是个极品废柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 想让自己一直保持清白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然事已至此 无论怎样你都会伤害其中一方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你越晚给出答案 伤害就会越深
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们三人中的任何人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便 我能再说一句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的烦恼太奢侈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 觅食了觅食了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我说的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们两个人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是漫画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处在放学后的教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会接吻什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要用姓称呼我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想输给姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一直在注视着谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道 却仍然去找姐姐商量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我想跟朋也君搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐虽然很吃惊 但还是马上笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说包在她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道她会那么说 也明白自己很卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也想待在朋也君身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能替代姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会变得像姐姐一样主动的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会留长头发 也会学习做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为朋也君心仪的女生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你做那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想待在朋也君身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤林…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 铃木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你交往的那些日子我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:19:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次明白被人需要是多么开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着能跟你很好地相处下去 就这样处下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一件最差劲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有了你 却还想着别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我注意到这事后 也没有告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我利用了你的温柔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你的头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椋跟我说「不要逃避」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想着一直保持这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜伤害椋也要选择你 这样卑鄙的事我不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她却说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这是不可能的」 「已经太晚了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果真的喜欢朋也 那就不能再逃避了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们不管怎样 总是会有人受到伤害的」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「毕竟我们喜欢上了同一个人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在一定在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的是…太晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是觉察 蒙混 还是面对都太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这将是最后一次伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是那孩子 我 还是朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果接受你的道歉 原谅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让我感觉这全都是假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把那段时光当作珍贵的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是开心的事 悲伤的事 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请你不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊 要去哪儿来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了要去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 那个取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为难得椋说想去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近可真是热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会不会觉得还是跟椋在一起更舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 我可要生气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我才能稍微安心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:22:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有点扭曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更直截了当一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夏天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
